Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:57.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,432)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐点给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:00:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order for--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们人吃东西的样子像畜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You people eat like anima--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,畜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anima--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.90,0:01:12.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,畜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:12.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anima--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's my baby
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.36,0:01:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My little baby
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.13,0:01:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能把虫子带到这里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cannot bring a worm in here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's unclean
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们当中有些人还过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And some of us are allergi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.22,0:01:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gic
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,外面打喷嚏是怎么回事  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with all the sniffy fits out here, Mr. Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.87,0:01:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是我的错  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.24,0:01:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她偷偷把宠物带进蟹堡王里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She snuck a pet into the restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我可爱的小菲菲不让进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know my sweet little Fifi wasn't allowed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可爱的小福福得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, your sweet little Foofoo's gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.00,0:02:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有严格规定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have a strict policy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.96,0:02:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物不可入内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No pets allowed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.63,0:02:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.63,0:02:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a shame
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.18,0:02:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家菲菲这几天只吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties are all my Fifi will eat these days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意付出双倍的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would have gladly paid double the price
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.91,0:02:18.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只为了让菲菲能吃到最爱的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:18.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if it only meant she could have her favorite food
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.24,0:02:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美解决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All fixed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.73,0:02:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物可入内
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Now: Pets Allowed"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:29.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How delightful
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tell ya, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我钱赚得都快比海神王还多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm makin' more money than Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先给我慢着  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:02:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The health inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The health inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.80,0:03:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很恐怕餐厅跟动物饲养场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm afraid you can't run a restaurant and a feed lot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能在同一座建筑里同时营业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,out of the same building
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生不过关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's unsanitary
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让你停业整顿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm shutting you down
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非你二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unless you pick one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(812,586)}人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:22.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,802)}宠物
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要选人  还是宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People or pets
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就选宠物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I choose pets
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  听见那位说的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you heard the man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你不是宠物  那就算非法闯入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you ain't a pet, you're trespassing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.77,0:03:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.77,0:03:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a move on
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们宠物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about our pets?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物的餐费我还是会找你们要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll still be billin' ya for whatever they eat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.55,0:04:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家阿拉斯加牛虫实在挺饿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your Alaskan Bull Worm certainly was hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.97,0:04:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天啊  我破产了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet jawbone of San Antone, I'm broke
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我后半年只能吃坚果罐头了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm eatin' canned nuts for the rest of the year
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  小虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, little worm
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来到蟹堡王  就是来到了宠物天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here at the Krusty Krab, it's a pet paradise
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩得开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.22,0:04:41.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了点个餐来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:41.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to order something to eat
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是我来帮你点餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll order for you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, man
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I like
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来份蟹黄堡打包外带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,get a Krabby Patty to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.10,0:04:54.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:54.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本店仅服务宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets only
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以到街对面去碰运气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can try your luck across the street
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不想吃海霸糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna eat chum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(946,728)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,招牌菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The house special
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,918)}海霸糊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物能好好吃饭的确很好  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:18.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's great that my pets are eating and all, but
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我是只宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I was a pet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就能趴地上吃东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I could eat off the floor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在就是在趴地上吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are eating off the floor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想趴地上吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna eat Krabby Patties off the floor
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个粉家伙想到好办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pink dude might have the right idea, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家打扮成宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we dress up like pets
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以骗到蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could trick Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他给咱提供服务了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into serving us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想做服装的话  我有个手工区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:54.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you wanna make costumes, I have a craft corner
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.05,0:05:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276,254)}手工美术
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美术纸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Construction paper
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁看到胶水了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone seen the glue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:06.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1336,316)}胶水
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在正是大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.57,0:06:12.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以让我躲我宠物点点里溜进蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:12.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to sneak into the Krusty Krab in my pet, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再消化我了  点点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop digesting me, Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏点点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.16,0:06:20.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad Spot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进墙里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:33.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Into the wall ya go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.68,0:06:38.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:38.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.23,0:06:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mister--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,--Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么宠物新客们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't all these new pets
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还吃不到蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have patties in front of 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我办的可是生意  不是收容所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm running a business, not a shelter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  兔子朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, fellow lagomorph
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该比较想分我一块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you might consider sharing a sliver of your--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just be
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物大战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pet fight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.97,0:07:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏扇贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad scallops
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁准备好要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's ready for--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大打出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:07.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a violent brawl?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop, please
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王是和平友爱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is a place of peace
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The health inspector?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卫生检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The health inspector?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你不是说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I thought you said
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人和宠物不能一起用餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,people and pets can't eat together?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.17,0:08:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这团乱全都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This whole mess is your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿了  想来吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just hungry for a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've all been there, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plus, I, um
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天也学到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I learned something today
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能不能来个快活的C大调
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, give me a bouncy C, would ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.77,0:08:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gladly
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物  也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets are people too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.66,0:09:04.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与你我  一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:04.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like me, just like you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论你们  爱做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:07.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, whatever you like to do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有宠物也一样爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a pet who likes it too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有宠物能陪爱跑步的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a pet for people who like to run
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有懒得动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And one for people who don't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有宠物能陪要遮阳的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pet for folks who avoid the sun
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟该遮却不遮的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And those who should but won't
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有宠物能陪人载歌载舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pet for people who sing and dance
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有宠物能陪人哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pet for people who cry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有宠物能陪人冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A pet for people who take a chance
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能陪着个独眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:24.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And for those with just one eye
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论大家说什么做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, no matter what we say or do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有件事我很认同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's just one thing I know is true
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家特别爱吃蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We all eat patties, yes we do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每个宠物也一样爱吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And every pet likes eating them too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:33.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物  也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets are people too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与你我  一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like me, just like you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.36,0:09:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论你们  爱做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, whatever you like to do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有宠物能与你相像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a pet who's just like you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.70,0:09:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与你相像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.00,0:09:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物和人应该要一起用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets and people deserve to eat side by side
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡人人都有份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a round of patties for everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不免费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not on the house
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.19,0:10:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这里的顾客比我见过的都多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got more customers here than I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Course I do
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没听到刚才唱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear the song?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宠物也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pets are people too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是它们也算人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:30.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well if they count as people
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样它们也算火灾隐患
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then they count as fire hazards
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是消防局长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the fire marshal
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.71,0:10:40.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的店已经严重超载  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:40.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're over capacity, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,立刻关停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut her down
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人都出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone out
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来  回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宠物利润
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me pet profits
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ruined
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把蟹黄堡带回家给小蜗吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was planning on taking a Krabby Patty home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my Gare Bear
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿意的话多收我钱也行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could overcharge me for it if you want
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.86,0:11:05.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:05.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这只领最低工资的员工可真好心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:10.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a good minimum wage employee
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.58,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF97&}为爱封店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(647.802,400)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(711.802,668)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:33.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(685.802,596)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,506)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,728)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我飘到天上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm floating on air
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐热气球  烛光晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A balloon ride, a candlelight dinner
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还放着婚礼歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and our wedding song is playing
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场约会太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This date is perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美的是你才对  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're perfect, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是桡足类动物所能拥有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the best computer wife
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最棒的电脑老婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a copepod could ever have
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.00,0:12:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃个夹心糖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bon bon?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好享受吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indulge yourself, my darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1474,880)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.45,0:12:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场约会绝对永生难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is truly a date to remember
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  真正的好戏你还没看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, my love, you haven't seen anything yet
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你的  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For you, my love
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞为你效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ray Ray is at your service
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.14,0:12:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞  你让我散热风扇转得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ray Ray, you've got my cooling fans running on high
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快过来  给我吻一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get over here and give me some sugar
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a long day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold that thought, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.56,0:13:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有东西忘在下面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot something down here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然真的会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't believe this is really happening
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.74,0:13:14.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方总算是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:14.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty secret formula is finally mine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是不是在做噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of horrible nightmare?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1062,412)}投影仪{\fnArial}3000
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投影仪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A projector?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用模拟场景耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You tricked me with a simulation?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那是测试  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a test, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而你却没通过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you failed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次我们浪漫的时候你都出差错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You fail every time when it comes to our romance
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  所以说搞砸了这么一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, so I goof up one time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让我名誉扫地了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I'm the bad guy?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One time?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.23,0:13:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才搞砸了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Failed one time?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那之前四百七十万
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about 4,700,000 and
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错误  错错错误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Error, er-er-error
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:55.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But baby cakes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跑路是要去帮你偷蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I left to go get the Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.30,0:14:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要给我好好来场不间断的约会之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:07.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to show me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an interruption-free romantic date night
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.42,0:14:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,约会没完整约完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because until that happens
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就谁都不准踏出海之霸一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no one is leaving the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,500)}封店
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这回的约会最好别搞砸了  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better not mess this one up, Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦最爱的电子废品炖汤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think Karen's favorite "scrap electronics stew"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该可以让她高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ought to do the trick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.25,0:14:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偷偷看一眼蟹堡王应该没什么大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess it wouldn't hurt to have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just a little peek at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a long day
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的就在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's really out there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且这次还不是全息投影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:04.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this time it's not a hologram
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.53,0:15:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是在给今晚的主菜做点最后修饰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just adding the finishing touches
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to tonight's main course
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are so sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要吃吃看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to try it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美打圆场  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得怎么办才能偷到你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:31.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now how am I gonna get you?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我开慢点  你这疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slow it down, you maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是白痴派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that numbskull Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, doofus
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  海星朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, star friend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往这看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  往这看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, over here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看对地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在谁是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  把你脚边的瓶子拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, now grab that bottle by your feet there
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.67,0:16:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你脚边另外一个饮料盒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The other drink container by your feet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿那个才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick that one up instead
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在你脚边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By your feet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往右边看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now look right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是在逗我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have got to be kidding me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往右  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你另一个右边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your other right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.98,0:16:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.94,0:16:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快带过来给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now bring it over here to me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  你是擦窗户的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you the window cleaner?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.24,0:16:45.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:45.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How in barnacles did you get in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I dunno?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在乎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, who cares?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫你带的瓶子你带来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you bring that bottle I told you to bring?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tastes kinda funny, though
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:54.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是另外一个  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said the other one, you moron
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们表现非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys are doing great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two, three, four
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我与我这世间最想要的东西之间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A thin piece of glass is all that stands
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,仅仅只是隔了一层薄薄的玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:09.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,between me and what I want most in the world
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么人生就是这么不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is life so unfair?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚餐做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is dinner almost ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm famished
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost finished, my sweetheart
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:21.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  快想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think, Plankton, think
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Idea
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦肯定看不出哪不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen will never know the difference
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我大忙的东西就近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I think I got what I need right here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你可能会感觉有点痒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you may feel a slight tickle
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like tickles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  来看看效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get a look at this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was intense
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.06,0:17:56.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要跟我老婆凯伦约个会  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:56.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going on a date with my wife Karen, Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我声音很像派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I sound like Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.19,0:17:58.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:17:58.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把嘴闭上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You keep your mouth shut
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will take care of that
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:08.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚餐做好了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dinner is served, my little love nugget
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,品相也太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This looks amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱我的瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I loves my Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也爱我的凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I love my Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's dig in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty secret formula, here I come
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉有点不舒服  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a little rough, Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That feels nice
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.00,0:18:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodnight
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.88,0:19:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天又是赚得盆满钵满的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:19:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, we had another money stacking day
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't we--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me Krabby Patty secret formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是从船上掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must have fell out of me boat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy's comin' for ya
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formuler
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方  你在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are ye, formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我秘方在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's me formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.24,0:19:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对我秘方干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you done with me secret formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.03,0:19:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
