Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formuler
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:33.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formuler?
