Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formuler
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.04,0:19:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在哪  秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you, formuler?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.97,0:19:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你偷了我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you have me formuler
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.05,0:19:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So just hand it over
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开门啊  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你偷了我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you've got me formuler
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁在敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who could that be?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘣嘣的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That banging noise?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烘干机而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just the dryer
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.55,0:20:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服让我先洗了  等下就不用麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd do the laundry so you wouldn't have to later
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kiss kiss
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是你说过最浪漫的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the most romantic thing you've ever said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方总算是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The formula is finally mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你在里面  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.21,0:20:24.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:24.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for holding it for me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天弥补了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today made up for everything
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我想给你点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I wanted to give you a little something
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,经过多年来的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After years of research
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最终综合了数据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally synthesized the data
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生成了蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and came up with the Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行啊  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.37,0:21:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁还用得着你的瓶装纸质版
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:21:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who needs your stupid hard copy in a bottle, anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在都有可以下载的电子版了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I have a downloadable version right here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:07.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.80,0:21:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.30,0:21:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密配方就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the secret formula is
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.17,0:21:16.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:16.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.85,0:21:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is what?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.35,0:21:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘方是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们哪一个是瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which one of us is Ray Ray?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am, you doofus
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我也是瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,well, I'm Ray Ray too
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我才是瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Ray Ray
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不稀罕谁才是真瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care who is the real one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.33,0:21:38.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩都得亲眼看我删掉秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:38.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can both watch this formula get deleted
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:39.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darling, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.83,0:21:43.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话好好说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:43.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, let's talk about this
