Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.96,0:21:49.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别搞砸约会之夜  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:49.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with date night, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.23,0:22:02.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这才是上好的约会  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:02.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now this is truly a wonderful date, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.19,0:22:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你把注意力全集中在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And thank you for giving me your undivided attention
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.36,0:22:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论如何我都会跟你好好浪漫  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't miss it for the world, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
